  "notes": [
    "This paper introduces a computational method called genetic Minimal Intervention Sets (gMIS) that extends beyond traditional synthetic lethality to include synthetic dosage lethality",
    "The method integrates genome-scale metabolic networks with regulatory pathways to predict lethal genetic interactions",
    "Key findings include identification of EZH2 as essential in hematological malignancies and context-dependent tumor suppressor genes"
  ]
